# Code owners for galdr.
#
# Syntax: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-customizations/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# galdr is maintained by a single person. This file exists so GitHub
# auto-requests a review on PRs touching the load-bearing invariants, and so
# branch-protection rules with "require review from code owners" cannot be
# bypassed for those paths.
#
# Ordering matters: later, more-specific rules override earlier ones.

# --- Default owner for everything not matched below ------------------------
*                                 @Arakiss

# --- Load-bearing invariants -----------------------------------------------
# The sensor must never break the agent session. The distiller must never
# reach off the loopback. Any edit here is an invariant-surface change.
/src/hook.rs                       @Arakiss
/src/main.rs                       @Arakiss
/src/ext.rs                        @Arakiss
/src/engine.rs                     @Arakiss
/src/daemon.rs                     @Arakiss
/src/ipc.rs                        @Arakiss
/src/catalog.rs                    @Arakiss

# --- Build, CI, release plumbing -------------------------------------------
/.github/workflows/                @Arakiss
/release-please-config.json        @Arakiss
/.release-please-manifest.json     @Arakiss
/deny.toml                         @Arakiss
/Cargo.toml                        @Arakiss
/Cargo.lock                        @Arakiss
/rust-toolchain.toml               @Arakiss

# --- Governance docs -------------------------------------------------------
/SECURITY.md                       @Arakiss
/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md                @Arakiss
/CONTRIBUTING.md                   @Arakiss
/.github/CODEOWNERS                @Arakiss
